{
  "id": "69aaccbb52ddd3d2504e9881",
  "title": "枯れた技術",
  "created": 1772801214,
  "updated": 1772801268,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69aaccbb52ddd3d2504e9881",
      "text": "枯れた技術",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801214,
      "updated": 1772801214
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccbe0000000000bc66de",
      "text": "[ふーことましろとひよりの会話]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801214,
      "updated": 1772801221
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccbf0000000000bc66df",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801215,
      "updated": 1772801215
    },
    {
      "id": "69aacccb0000000000bc66e0",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801227,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66e1",
      "text": "ねえねえ今日のテーマ、「枯れた技術」ね！🌵",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66e2",
      "text": "なんかさ、字面だけ見ると「古くて終わった技術？」って感じするけど、実はぜんぜん違うんだよね。ネットでもよく出てくるワード。まずはここからいこー。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66e3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66e4",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66e5",
      "text": "ふふ、たしかに言葉だけだと少しさみしい印象がありますよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66e6",
      "text": "でも実際には「長いあいだ使われて、信頼できるようになった技術」という意味なんですよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66e7",
      "text": "いろんな人が使って、問題点がだいたい出尽くしているから、安心して使えるもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66e8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66e9",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66ea",
      "text": "概ねその理解で正しい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66eb",
      "text": "技術は登場直後がいちばん不安定。バグや設計ミスが残っている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66ec",
      "text": "時間が経つと、多くの実運用によって問題が洗い出される。修正される。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66ed",
      "text": "結果として「予測可能な技術」になる。それを枯れた技術と呼ぶ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66ee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66ef",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66f0",
      "text": "おー、「予測可能」ってワードいいね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66f1",
      "text": "つまり「だいたいどう動くか分かるやつ」ってことか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66f2",
      "text": "新技術ってさ、正直ワクワクするけど地雷も多いじゃん？ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66f3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66f4",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66f5",
      "text": "その通り。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66f6",
      "text": "例えば新しいプログラミング言語。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66f7",
      "text": "性能は高いが、ライブラリ（便利ツール集）が少ない。情報も少ない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66f8",
      "text": "不具合が見つかる可能性も高い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66f9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66fa",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66fb",
      "text": "ああ、それってスマホの新しいアプリみたいですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66fc",
      "text": "出たばかりのときは不具合が多くて、アップデートを重ねて少しずつ安定していく、みたいな。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66fd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66fe",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc66ff",
      "text": "わかりみ～。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6700",
      "text": "ゲームでも「初期バージョンはバグ祭り」ってあるあるだしｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6701",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6702",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6703",
      "text": "対して枯れた技術は、情報量が多い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6704",
      "text": "ドキュメント、解説記事、過去の事例。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6705",
      "text": "問題が起きても、だいたい解決方法が見つかる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6706",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6707",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6708",
      "text": "あー、「ググったら答え出てくる率高い技術」って感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6709",
      "text": "それ神じゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc670a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc670b",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc670c",
      "text": "かなり近い定義。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc670d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc670e",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc670f",
      "text": "でも、少し気になるのは……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6710",
      "text": "枯れた技術ばかり使うと、新しいものが生まれにくくなったりしませんか？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6711",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6712",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6713",
      "text": "あ、それ私もちょっと思った！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6714",
      "text": "全部「安定第一」でいったら、世界ずっと同じじゃね？みたいな。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6715",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6716",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6717",
      "text": "いい指摘。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6718",
      "text": "実際、技術開発はバランスが重要。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6719",
      "text": " 新技術：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc671a",
      "text": "  高性能の可能性",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc671b",
      "text": "  革新",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc671c",
      "text": " 枯れた技術：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc671d",
      "text": "  安定",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc671e",
      "text": "  低リスク",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc671f",
      "text": "用途によって使い分ける。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6720",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6721",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6722",
      "text": "たとえば、どういうところで枯れた技術が向いているんですか？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6723",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6724",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6725",
      "text": "人命や社会インフラ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6726",
      "text": "鉄道、医療機器、金融システムなど。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6727",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6728",
      "text": "これらは「新しいけど不安定」より",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6729",
      "text": "「少し古くても確実」のほうが重要。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc672a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc672b",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc672c",
      "text": "あーーーなるほど！！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc672d",
      "text": "電車の制御システムとかで「最新ベータ版です！」とか言われたら怖すぎるｗｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc672e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc672f",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6730",
      "text": "ふふ、本当ですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6731",
      "text": "「ちゃんと長く使われてきたもの」が安心ですよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6732",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6733",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6734",
      "text": "だから任天堂の有名な考え方がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6735",
      "text": "「[枯れた技術の水平思考]」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6736",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6737",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6738",
      "text": "お、出た！ゲーム界隈でたまに聞くやつ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6739",
      "text": "でも正直ちゃんと理解してない勢です。解説よろ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc673a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc673b",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc673c",
      "text": "簡単に言う。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc673d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc673e",
      "text": "新しい技術を作るのではなく、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc673f",
      "text": "既に安定した技術を、新しい使い方で組み合わせる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6740",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6741",
      "text": "例：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6742",
      "text": "Wii",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6743",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6744",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6745",
      "text": "あ、リモコンみたいなコントローラーのゲーム機ですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6746",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6747",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6748",
      "text": "そう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6749",
      "text": "使っているセンサー技術自体は特別新しくない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc674a",
      "text": "しかし「体を動かして遊ぶゲーム」という形にした。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc674b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc674c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc674d",
      "text": "あーーー！！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc674e",
      "text": "たしかに！！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc674f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6750",
      "text": "技術自体は地味でも",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6751",
      "text": "アイデアで神ゲーになるってことか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6752",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6753",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6754",
      "text": "正確。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6755",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6756",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6757",
      "text": "なんだか素敵ですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6758",
      "text": "新しいものを無理に作るだけじゃなくて、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6759",
      "text": "今あるものを上手に活かす考え方。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc675a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc675b",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc675c",
      "text": "わかる。なんか高校の文化祭みたい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc675d",
      "text": "道具は普通でも、アイデアで神企画になるやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc675e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc675f",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6760",
      "text": "例えとしては悪くない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6761",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6762",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6763",
      "text": "ふふ、ひよりさんにしては珍しくやわらかい評価ですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6764",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6765",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6766",
      "text": "レア台詞きたｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6767",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6768",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6769",
      "text": "……否定するほどではない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc676a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc676b",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc676c",
      "text": "で、今日のまとめいくよー。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc676d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc676e",
      "text": "枯れた技術ってのは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc676f",
      "text": " 古い＝ダメじゃない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6770",
      "text": " むしろ実績あって安定",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6771",
      "text": " 新しいアイデアと組み合わせると強い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6772",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6773",
      "text": "って感じ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6774",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6775",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6776",
      "text": "安心できる技術と、新しい発想。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6777",
      "text": "その組み合わせが大切なんですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6778",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6779",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc677a",
      "text": "結論としてはそれ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc677b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc677c",
      "text": "技術の価値は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc677d",
      "text": "「新しいかどうか」ではなく",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc677e",
      "text": "「目的に合っているか」で決まる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc677f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6780",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6781",
      "text": "おおー、なんか最後いい感じにまとまった！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6782",
      "text": "じゃあ次のテーマどうする？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6783",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6784",
      "text": "「AI」とか？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    },
    {
      "id": "69aaccf30000000000bc6785",
      "text": "それとも「黒歴史プログラミング言語」とか？ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772801268,
      "updated": 1772801268
    }
  ]
}